    Description

    About SC Mobile: The new and improved SC mobile app offers a fast, secure, and user-friendly mobile banking experience, designed to take care of its customers banking needs on the go anytime, anywhere ! Indulge in effortless app interface to get customized alerts, quick access to statements, dashboards, cards management, making online bank transfers & much more. Prime features & services: Home with Glance: With just one swipe, get access to all your financial transactions. Transfer funds, pay bills, manage your accounts and cards from the home screen, view account balances in real-time and much more! Fast, Secure & Easy Access: Enhances digital security enables you to login with touch/face ID without the need of PIN or password New modern look and feel with simplified navigation and faster loading times so that banking becomes a quick and easy experience. QR Pay: Make the best of the QR pay for quick & easy payments at merchant Hassel-free Payment: Transfer funds instantly between your SC account or other accounts by selecting Local Transfer & other payment methods; Add beneficiary at ease and transfer funds without registering a beneficiary (RAAST). Manage Cards Easily: Apply for a credit card right from the app, pay credit card bills & even block/hotlist credit or debit card. All Products under one roof: Enjoy the convenience of digital banking at your fingertips, open & apply for Cards, Accounts, Fixed Deposits & term Deposits and other product offerings in the market without any hassle. Effortless & Convenient Bill Payments: Pay utility bills, Credit Card bills, Electricity bills, Insurance bill & Mobile bills & pay for recharge, instantly. Even set up scheduled funds transfer and set standing orders so you don’t miss any payment. Insta Account Opening: Non-SC Bank customers can now Open an account in a few simple steps. Download the app and click on open an account today! And SC Bank customers can apply for product of their choice with their data pre-filled for the convenience of easy application submission. Locate us: Locate nearest Standard Chartered ATM or Branch by just over a click Other Services: Our new services on SC Mobile App allow you to bank on your fingertips without having to visit a branch or calling the client centre. Register for SC Mobile today and enjoy unlimited convenience. Learn more on the new release:



    ^ Order a Cheque Book & Activate – You can order a cheque book through SC Mobile and receive at your mailing address. You can also activate your cheque book through the app.
    ^ Stop Cheque – You can instantly stop your cheques , single or multiple, or the entire cheque book through the app. We strive to keep your finances safe and secure.
    ^ Manage Debit Card – Control your card usage at your convenience. Choose yourself to enable/disable channels or increase/decrease your limits – all in just a few taps.
    ^ Debit Card issuance – order a new card or replace damaged card on your fingertips
    ^ Credit Card Block and Replacement – Credit Card lost or stolen? You can now block your Credit Card instantly and get it replaced through the app.
    ^ Signature Capture – New to bank? Want to update your signature? You can add or update your signature for all your accounts through the app.
    ^ Pay Order – Request for Pay Order through SC Mobile App, save yourself a trip to branch.
    ^ Bank Certificates – Request for Account maintenance, Withholding tax, PRC certificates from SC Mobile App & receive at your email address!

    New version not working on my iPhone 11 Pro Max

    It’s been more than one month now since this app stopped working on my phone. The last version was working alright since many years. I called SC priority number in Karachi several times but to no avail. Instead each time they would insist that it’s just working fine. I have no clue who to contact now. On my laptop, the online version is working alright with the same ID and password. It’s so frustrating.

    Developer Response ,

    Hi Shakeel , please do write us regarding your concern at complaints.pakistan@sc.com with your contact details and the Case #860444 you may also write us on Facebook at https://www.facebook.com/standardcharteredpk/ , or call us at 021-111-002-002 .

    shah_02 , 06/10/2022

    Much better experience

    The new experience solves a lot of problems. Still few pain points like no option to search while making a transfer. You've to scroll and look at each one by one. Imagine having 100 of accounts to look through.
    I'd love to see quick transfers based on recents.

    Developer Response ,

    Hello shah_02 , we have shared your feedback with our team that is continuously working to improve your banking experience .Your feedback is very valuable to us. Stay tuned and enjoy the convenience of banking with SC Mobile.

    Tsani1957 , 07/16/2022

    SCB’s New App

    The new app is confusing and while swiping a transfer you don’t get a chance to review what you’re paying. The number font is too large. It’s a confusing app and makes me nervous when I am transferring money withh just one swipe. The older app was much much better.

    Developer Response ,

    Hello Tsani1957, thank you for reaching out, you are requested to please follow the below step

    To make your font size smaller or larger:
    1. Open your device's Settings app.
    2. Select Accessibility Text and display.
    3. Select Font size.
    4. Use the slider to choose your font size.
